<Document>
  <name>Hardeman County — Unmapped Historical Markers</name>
  <description>THC markers in Hardeman County without an HMDB id (isMissing excluded). 4 with THC coords; 0 geocoded from address; 1 omitted (no usable address).</description>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Goodlett Cemetery</name>
